data.description:
Cozy home nestled up in an established neighborhood. This home provides endless opportunities with an oversized split backyard, a great place to add a pool, and still plenty of room for pets. The kitchen provides a drop-in gas stove and plenty of counter space. The kitchen has a direct view into the living room so you will never miss a beat when entertaining. The primary bedroom features a bay window with plenty of space for a sitting area or desk. The primary bathroom has a walk-in closet, a linen closet, a garden tub, and a stand-alone shower. This home will have plenty of room for any stage of your family's life. 
New Roof 2020, AC serviced, fresh paint throughout common areas.
